properties.Name: ComponentMaintenance
properties.Description:
Periodic expenditures undertaken to preserve or retain a component for its original use.

Maintenance does not improve or extend the life of the component.

Maintenance is an expense and are not capitalized.

Columns.Name: ComponentMaintenanceId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Component Maintenance.

Columns.Name: ComponentId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Component.

Columns.Name: MaintenanceOperationId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a maintenance operation.

Columns.Name: MaintenanceTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Maintenance Type.

Columns.Name: MaintenancePlannedStartTimestamp
Columns.Description: The planned start timestamp of the maintenance.

Columns.Name: MaintenancePlannedEndTimestamp
Columns.Description: The planned end timestamp of the maintenance.

Columns.Name: MaintenanceActualStartTimestamp
Columns.Description: The actual start timestamp of the maintenance.

Columns.Name: MaintenanceActualEndTimestamp
Columns.Description: The actual end timestamp of the maintenance.

Columns.Name: MaintenanceEstimatedCost
Columns.Description: The estimated cost of the Maintenance Operation.

Columns.Name: MaintenanceActualCost
Columns.Description: The actual cost of the Maintenance Operation.

Columns.Name: MaintenanceNote
Columns.Description: Notes, comments or additional information regarding the Maintenance performed.
